query:
SELECT jurisdiction_id AS jurisdiction_id,
       geojson AS geojson
FROM
  (SELECT jurisdiction_id,
          jsonb_build_object('type', 'Feature', 'id', jurisdiction_id, 'geometry', ST_AsGeoJSON(jurisdiction_geometry)::jsonb, 'properties', to_jsonb(row) - 'jurisdiction_id' - 'jurisdiction_geometry') AS geojson
   FROM
     (SELECT jurisdiction_id,
             jurisdiction_name,
             jurisdiction_parent_id,
             jurisdiction_geometry
      FROM plans_materialzied_view) row) AS expr_qry
WHERE jurisdiction_id = '3951'
LIMIT 10000;
